title: Restaurant.Divided.S01E01.WS.DSR.x264-[NY2]
description: a reality series that pits two warring factions in a failing, family-run restaurant - each with a different vision of how to save it - against each other to determine who has the best plan. After dividing the entire restaurant space in half, each group is given a limited time and budget to transform their space into their vision for a new restaurant. Then, the two restaurants open and compete, side-by-side, by serving real customers over a period of two nights. The concept that does best overall in customer reviews, critic reviews and profitability will be the one that unites the restaurant again.
